text.tspan: Waiting on Thee, Lord, waiting on Thee
Waiting on Thee, Lord, waiting on Thee;
While here with Thee I stay,
Waiting on Thee, waiting on Thee.
Waiting on Thee, Lord, waiting on Thee;
Waiting on Thee, waiting on Thee.
Waiting on Thee, Lord, waiting on Thee;
Make me Thy will to know,
Help me Thy way to go,

Waiting on Thee, waiting on Thee.
Waiting on Thee, Lord, waiting on Thee;

Waiting on Thee, waiting on Thee.
